Logs.Text: I asked about "Dental Coverage." Mr. Krabs turned purple, shouted "Me Money!" and hyperventilated. Application immediately terminated.

Description: High-pressure culinary environment. Responsibilities include managing the grill during the lunch rush (anchovies), defending the Secret Formula from Plankton, and ensuring Mr. Krabs makes a profit of at least 110%. Must provide own spatula.
Notes: Dodged a bullet. The coworker next to me (Squidward) looked miserable and was playing a clarinet very poorly.

Result.Reason: Candidate requested a starting wage above $0.00/hr. Hiring Manager (Mr. Krabs) laughed until he cried, then kicked candidate out.
